  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc7\u0bb7\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We will work with dedication for the people of the country - Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "We will work with dedication for the people of the country. The law will be fully enforced to protect democracy. Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena said that no one can act against democracy.",
        "He mentioned the above in a comment to the media following his swearing in as Prime Minister today in the presence of President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The government has taken appropriate measures to solve the basic problems found in the social structure with the support of friendly countries and international organizations. Fuel and gas service infrastructure will be optimally distributed.",
        "Let us work with dedication to the people of the country. If the economic crisis is solved, other problems in the social structure will naturally disappear.",
        "Even though the policy has changed politically, we are united for the country. We will work with dedication for the country. We will properly implement the law to ensure democracy.",
        "He said that the political and social change expected by the people of the country will be brought about. No one can be allowed to act contrary to democracy. We have called on all the political parties to work together."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Dinesh Gunawardena",
          "label": "PERSON"
        }
